---
title: Creamy Garlic Chicken Breast and Spinach with Smashed Potatoes
description: Tonight's dinner is restaurant worthy! A quick and effortless creamy garlic spinach sauce is draped over golden seared chicken and equally delectable smashed potatoes!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poitrines-de-poulet-et-sauce-cremeuse-a-lail-et-aux-epinards-6ad90a76.jpg
